import React from 'react';
import { Button } from '../../globalStyles';
import { GiCrystalBars } from 'react-icons/gi';
import { GiCutDiamond, GiRock } from 'react-icons/gi';
import { IconContext } from 'react-icons/lib';
import {
  MusicSection,
  MusicWrapper,
  MusicHeading,
  MusicContainer,
  MusicCard,
  MusicCardInfo,
  MusicCardIcon,
  MusicCardPlan,
  MusicCardCost,
  MusicCardLength,
  MusicCardFeatures,
  MusicCardFeature
} from './Music.elements';

function Music() {
  return (
    <IconContext.Provider value={{ color: '#a9b3c1', size: 64 }}>
      <MusicSection>
        <MusicWrapper>
          <MusicHeading>MUSIC</MusicHeading>
          <MusicContainer>
            <MusicCard to='/music'>
              <MusicCardInfo>
                <MusicCardIcon>
                  <GiRock />
                </MusicCardIcon>
                <MusicCardPlan>The Beatles</MusicCardPlan>
                <MusicCardCost>$99.99</MusicCardCost>
                <MusicCardLength>per month</MusicCardLength>
                <MusicCardFeatures>
                  <MusicCardFeature>100 New Users</MusicCardFeature>
                  <MusicCardFeature>$10,000 Budget</MusicCardFeature>
                  <MusicCardFeature>Retargeting analytics</MusicCardFeature>
                </MusicCardFeatures>
                <Button primary>Choose Plan</Button>
              </MusicCardInfo>
            </MusicCard>
            <MusicCard to='/sign-up'>
              <MusicCardInfo>
                <MusicCardIcon>
                  <GiCrystalBars />
                </MusicCardIcon>
                <MusicCardPlan>Gold Rush</MusicCardPlan>
                <MusicCardCost>$299.99</MusicCardCost>
                <MusicCardLength>per month</MusicCardLength>
                <MusicCardFeatures>
                  <MusicCardFeature>1000 New Users</MusicCardFeature>
                  <MusicCardFeature>$50,000 Budget</MusicCardFeature>
                  <MusicCardFeature>Lead Gen Analytics</MusicCardFeature>
                </MusicCardFeatures>
                <Button primary>Choose Plan</Button>
              </MusicCardInfo>
            </MusicCard>
            <MusicCard to='/sign-up'>
              <MusicCardInfo>
                <MusicCardIcon>
                  <GiCutDiamond />
                </MusicCardIcon>
                <MusicCardPlan>Diamond Kings</MusicCardPlan>
                <MusicCardCost>$999.99</MusicCardCost>
                <MusicCardLength>per month</MusicCardLength>
                <MusicCardFeatures>
                  <MusicCardFeature>Unlimited Users</MusicCardFeature>
                  <MusicCardFeature>Unlimited Budget</MusicCardFeature>
                  <MusicCardFeature>24/7 Support</MusicCardFeature>
                </MusicCardFeatures>
                <Button primary>Choose Plan</Button>
              </MusicCardInfo>
            </MusicCard>
          </MusicContainer>
        </MusicWrapper>
      </MusicSection>
    </IconContext.Provider>
  );
}
export default Music;
